{"tid":780340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧龍威案有轉機 領事館取得菲律賓官方入境紀錄","createTime":"2018-08-15T05:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T11:38:16.000Z","uid":162324,"like":41,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe05f616619c7ce83e795f0bb4ea763ffb31612","tid":780340,"uid":162324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:39:50.000Z","msg":"港人鄧龍威18年前在菲律賓被捲販毒案，被判罪成及終身監禁，今日是提交上訴書的「死線」。立法會議員謝偉俊透露，中國駐菲律賓領事館昨日從菲律賓移民局，取得鄧龍威入境菲律賓的官方紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊將會在今日下午4時半，與鄧龍威的家屬到入境處總部，領取有關鄧龍威於2000年6月19日入境菲律賓的記錄，再研究上訴工作。<br />\n<br />\n由於鄧一直堅持是含冤入獄，若沒有本港入境處發出其出入境紀錄作新證據，恐無法上訴。特首林鄭月娥早前去信菲律賓總統杜特爾特，要求正視鄧龍威一案，及責成菲律賓移民局，提供鄧於2000年入境菲律賓記錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然唔鍾意林鄭 但今次確實多得佢出手呢單野先有轉機"},{"pid":"a43c9446bf3456e174a19f5506dcd360093a61ed","tid":780340,"uid":162324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:41:39.000Z","msg":"link：<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1291794/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1291794%2F&d=bzEgjJDypzABWqFO%2B20nl8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=76bb6ee8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1291794%2F&h=47130894\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1291794/</a>"},{"pid":"d556eaaa4c2a744ed557ed69dc96281b8127dfba","tid":780340,"uid":13503,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"申冤申左18年今日走黎多謝林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25c631d55517fd0392a5a0faf4d3fd2b599251f","tid":780340,"uid":173617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T05:43:13.000Z","msg":"真係判錯會賠幾多錢?"},{"pid":"d5c1bb474ff3d9c1863e28cd152e213986cc971e","tid":780340,"uid":81113,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"d556eaaa4c2a744ed557ed69dc96281b8127dfba","tid":780340,"uid":